snippet.textDisplay:
This is not what coke studio use to be.

Simplicity was its beauty.

All these star faces , and visual effects was never required.

Coke studio was all about seeing instruments, musicians all those high tech music devices. We felt closer to music that way.

Please bring back that era again.

Almost after 6 years, we were not expecting this.
